metadata.name: The Ghost Queen
metadata.description:
This illustration I made last September. Tradi x digital illustration. 

"the ghost queen who was in my dream that at that time I often dreamed about.  She looks like she's soaking in the darkness with a pretty face and a scary look staring at me.  With a dress and accessories that are shiny white silver.  He was also Surrounded by an evil power with black liquid and many ghost hands appeared around him, I'm not sure what it was but that's what I felt at that time."

Canvas size : 3000 x 4000 px
